Task-5
Collect two strings from user
string1: wikipedia
string2: typescript
output: p  +  c   ===> ascii value of p + ascii value of c  ====>  198
(ord , chr)

str1 = input ("Enter the string1:")
str2 = input("Enter the string2:")
middle_character_1 = ((len(str1)//2))
g = (str1[middle_character_1])
print(g)
middle_character_2 = ((len(str2)//2))
h = (str2[middle_character_2])
print(h)
a = ord(g)
print(a)
b = ord(h)
print(b)
print("Addition of ascii value str1 and str2 is:", a + b)
