Task10:
Mutation

str1 = input("Enter the string1:") #: abracadabra
a = list(str1)
a[5] = 'k'
str1 = ''.join(a)
print(str1)  # output: abrackdabra
# Another method
str2 = input("Enter the string:") # input:prokram
print(str2[:3] +"g" + str2[4:])   # output:program
